<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEACE HARD TO KEEP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Does peace have a chance? Yes. Peace has been given a chance many times, and it 
will come around hopefully without bloodshed. 
</P>
<P>
Are we going to keep it? No. We didn't keep it after WWI, WWII and the Korean 
War. We start wars, but we do not keep peace. Not for long. We still don't know 
how. 
</P>
<P>
SOPHIE BINGHAM 
</P>
<P>
Laguna Hills 
</P>
</TEXT>
