<P>
DEMOCRATS' ENDORSEMENTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Santa Monica Democratic Club will make its official endorsements for 
candidates and ballot measures in the November local and state elections 
Wednesday at 7:30 p.m. at the John Muir School auditorium, 721 Ocean Park Blvd. 
</P>
<P>
Democratic candidates for City Council, Rent Control Board, Santa Monica-Malibu 
Unified School District board of education and Community College board of 
trustees have been invited to make presentations, as have representatives of 
nine local ballot measures, according to club President Mildred Rosenstein. 
</P>
<P>
