FORCES -- KUWAIT; RELOCATION OF PEOPLE; IRAQ -- BORDERS -- KUWAIT; HUSSEIN, 
SADDAM; EVACUATIONS; IRAQIS -- KUWAIT; PALESTINIANS -- KUWAIT; KUWAIT -- 
ELECTIONS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; IRAQ -- FOREIGN 
POPULATIONS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
