SPEECHES; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN POLICY; MILITARY STRATEGY; FUND RAISING; 
POLITICAL CANDIDATES; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS; WILSON, PETE; CALIFORNIA GOVERNOR; 
ECONOMIC SANCTIONS; SUMMIT CONFERENCES; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- 
USSR; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- PERSIAN GULF 
</P>
