<SUBJECT>
<P>
WILLIAMS, JOHN (HOT ROD); SEATTLE SUPERSONICS (BASKETBALL TEAM); CLEVELAND 
CAVALIERS (BASKETBALL TEAM) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA092090-0178 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 279022 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 20, 1990, Thursday, Home Edition 
